{"type": "article", "id": 22386, "title": "带工作台的座椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-17T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160206vIOQws8rtCpejnB4.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款带工作台的座椅，是从瑞典设计师 Thomas Bernstrand 、Stefan Borselius 和 Johan Lindau 的扶手椅 HONKEN 中变化出来的。椅子本身是由不锈钢和金属网格制作，搭配 4 根细橡木腿，增加的部分是一些组件，包括“L”型或方形的木质工作台面，柜子，电源和一个脚凳，可以任意安装以满足个性需求。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160204VIYAZixTNgQ92zCO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160204wDSQdyH7mzY9F354.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81418093\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160205HZiRy8W6bau9VcnS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84474328\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160205Gmjs6IEFuMA8Y3w5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84474328\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}